</tr>
</table>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://viewfinder.english-heritage.org.uk/" class="external text" title="http://viewfinder.english-heritage.org.uk/" rel="nofollow">Historic images of Crystal Palace, dating back to the 1850s, held by the National Monuments Record, the public archive of English Heritage.</a> Search on Crystal Palace to view.</li>
